<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms and Conditions</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .doc-meta {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .doc-meta strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .toc {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .toc-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .toc ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .toc li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .clause {
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .clause-header {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .clause p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .clause ul,
        .clause ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .clause li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .highlight-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .warning-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #991b1b;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="doc-title">Terms & Conditions</div>
        <div class="doc-meta"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{effectiveDate}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Last
                Updated:</strong> {{#if lastUpdated}}{{lastUpdated}}{{else}}{{effectiveDate}}{{/if}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Welcome to {{companyName}}. These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your use of our services, products,
            and website. By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms. Please read them
            carefully.</p>

        <div class="toc">
            <div class="toc-title">Table of Contents</div>
            <ol>
                <li>Definitions</li>
                <li>Acceptance of Terms</li>
                <li>Services Description</li>
                <li>User Obligations</li>
                <li>Payment & Billing</li>
                <li>Intellectual Property</li>
                <li>Privacy & Data Protection</li>
                <li>Limitation of Liability</li>
                <li>Indemnification</li>
                <li>Termination</li>
                <li>Governing Law</li>
                <li>Contact Information</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">1. Definitions</div>
            <p>In these Terms, the following definitions apply:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>"Company"</strong> refers to {{companyName}}, located at {{{companyAddress}}}.</li>
                <li><strong>"Services"</strong> refers to all products, applications, tools, and features provided by
                    the Company.</li>
                <li><strong>"User"</strong> refers to any individual or entity that accesses or uses the Services.</li>
                <li><strong>"Content"</strong> refers to all text, data, information, documents, and materials generated
                    or processed through the Services.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">2. Acceptance of Terms</div>
            <p>By accessing or using our Services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound
                by these Terms, as well as our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, you
                must immediately discontinue use of the Services.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement. If you are accepting on
                    behalf of an organization, you represent that you have authority to bind that organization.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">3. Services Description</div>
            <p>{{companyName}} provides {{#if serviceDescription}}{{{serviceDescription}}}{{else}}professional document
                generation, management, and automation services designed for businesses and individuals{{/if}}. The
                Company reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the Services at any time with
                reasonable notice.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">4. User Obligations</div>
            <p>As a user of our Services, you agree to:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration and maintain its accuracy.
                </li>
                <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials and notify us immediately of any unauthorized
                    access.</li>
                <li>Use the Services only for lawful purposes and in compliance with all applicable laws and
                    regulations.</li>
                <li>Not reproduce, duplicate, copy, sell, resell, or exploit any portion of the Services without express
                    written permission.</li>
                <li>Not attempt to gain unauthorized access to any systems, networks, or data associated with the
                    Services.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">5. Payment & Billing</div>
            <p>Certain features of our Services may require payment of fees. By subscribing to a paid plan, you agree to
                pay all applicable fees as described. All fees are non-refundable unless otherwise stated. The Company
                reserves the right to modify pricing with {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}}
                prior notice.</p>
            <p>Payments shall be inclusive of all applicable taxes including GST. Late payments may result in suspension
                of Services and attract interest at the rate of 1.5% per month on outstanding amounts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">6. Intellectual Property</div>
            <p>All intellectual property rights in the Services, including but not limited to software, designs,
                trademarks, and documentation, are owned by {{companyName}} or its licensors. Users retain ownership of
                their content but grant the Company a limited license to process, store, and display such content solely
                for providing the Services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">7. Privacy & Data Protection</div>
            <p>We are committed to protecting your privacy. Our collection, use, and disclosure of personal information
                is governed by our Privacy Policy. By using our Services, you consent to the data practices described
                therein. We comply with applicable data protection laws including the Information Technology Act, 2000
                and the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">8. Limitation of Liability</div>
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p><strong>Important:</strong> To the maximum extent permitted by law, {{companyName}} shall not be
                    liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not
                    limited to loss of profits, data, or business opportunities, regardless of the cause of action.</p>
            </div>
            <p>The Company's total aggregate liability under these Terms shall not exceed the amount paid by you to the
                Company in the twelve (12) months preceding the event giving rise to the claim.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">9. Indemnification</div>
            <p>You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless {{companyName}}, its officers, directors, employees,
                and agents from and against any claims, damages, obligations, losses, liabilities, costs, or debt
                arising from your use of the Services or violation of these Terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">10. Termination</div>
            <p>Either party may terminate these Terms at any time. The Company may suspend or terminate your access to
                the Services immediately, without prior notice, for conduct that violates these Terms or is harmful to
                the Company, other users, or third parties. Upon termination, your right to use the Services will
                immediately cease.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">11. Governing Law</div>
            <p>These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes arising
                out of or in connection with these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in
                {{#if jurisdiction}}{{jurisdiction}}{{else}}Bangalore, Karnataka, India{{/if}}.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <div class="clause-header">12. Contact Information</div>
            <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
            <p><strong>{{companyName}}</strong><br>
                {{{companyAddress}}}<br>
                {{#if companyEmail}}Email: {{companyEmail}}<br>{{/if}}
                {{#if companyPhone}}Phone: {{companyPhone}}{{/if}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>© {{#if currentYear}}{{currentYear}}{{else}}2024{{/if}} {{companyName}}. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>These Terms and Conditions were last updated on {{effectiveDate}}.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>